93
00:06:08,739 --> 00:06:12,139
So, that's the one that was found near the car.

94
00:06:12,139 --> 00:06:15,939
No, if that's included, then there are two missing in total.

95
00:06:16,939 --> 00:06:20,939
Then did the remaining one burn in the car to ashes?

96
00:06:20,939 --> 00:06:23,039
Or...

97
00:06:24,239 --> 00:06:25,439
Conan.

