Darn. What the heck is going on anyway?

122
00:07:50,039 --> 00:07:51,239
Darn!

123
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:56,339
Hey. It's about time you really cool it, Banba.

124
00:07:56,339 --> 00:08:00,139
You understand that you're in a grave predicament, don't you?

125
00:08:00,139 --> 00:08:02,339
Hatsune burns to death in a car

126
00:08:02,339 --> 00:08:04,539
that is parked in the parking lot of this restaurant,

127
00:08:04,539 --> 00:08:07,039
and on the fake nail that was found near that car,

128
00:08:07,039 --> 00:08:10,239
skin that looked to be like that of the culprit was stuck to it.

129
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:14,239
The DNA of the skin virtually matched the DNA of your hair

130
